{"tid":493550,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得人類本身唔屬於地球？","createTime":"2017-12-08T15:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T04:56:44.000Z","uid":8118,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8cacb68aa44992ca69a7b006006d8d9639d3aec6","tid":493550,"uid":8118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"人類唔著衫會凍死<br />\n又可以以長時間曬住<br />\n又唔見其他動物係咁"},{"pid":"8f81c1cdb7708b0a3c303060eb01b965ff4810a1","tid":493550,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"唔去凍的地方咪得"},{"pid":"5c6e690dd877c6580d4bc525d67b4e50421c98a5","tid":493550,"uid":78978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"你開心就好"},{"pid":"7ce2f8c44b034637545794ab7cea971139dd8b24","tid":493550,"uid":57418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔去凍的地方咪得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解，人類原本起源非洲"},{"pid":"029f7a62ca74c3b38914b94710cb79fba25ff741","tid":493550,"uid":38988,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔去凍的地方咪得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解，人類原本起源非洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每60秒"},{"pid":"505087e73579e4cf267d6e723ce0ec0f7924b7a4","tid":493550,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:49:58.000Z","msg":"係咪調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b519506a0b781a4df0e6c6214b708642387196f9","tid":493550,"uid":138792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類唔著衫會凍死<br />\n又可以以長時間曬住<br />\n又唔見其他動物係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為係舊石器時代 原始人已經識運用火<br />\n亦會用獸皮為衣服 禦寒能力都唔差<br />\n太陽曬亦會搵到陰暗位 避暑<br />\n人類自身嘅不足靠智力嚟補償係人類最大嘅本事<br />\n所以先企係食物鏈嘅頂點<br />\n<br />\nbtw 候鳥會隨季節遷徙<br />\n某d生物就會冬眠<br />\n因為佢地都會覺得凍 會有生物特定嘅活動範圍<br />\n但全世界都有人類嘅足跡 <br />\n咁點解人類唔屬於地球<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a99781372883dc2609d5275cab85f195673ea5","tid":493550,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"prometheus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93920e01e49ddb63a6af004d6bfd4742196990ab","tid":493550,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"人類有智商,可運用智慧改變生活方式"},{"pid":"002f9653a5b94edac6b88bdf33e92155a140df9e","tid":493550,"uid":60136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔去凍的地方咪得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解，人類原本起源非洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每60秒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有，因為你只想到你自己。"},{"pid":"5694319cd53e32cb75f4039de7d2d0d828dada87","tid":493550,"uid":117894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"頭髮"},{"pid":"d2595959087d79ba95e7e3594a359305cca7cb31","tid":493550,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類唔著衫會凍死<br />\n又可以以長時間曬住<br />\n又唔見其他動物係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但基因分析，人類基因和動物好接近，點睇？<br />\n<br />\n人類由動物演化而成，又點睇？"},{"pid":"805dcdd190711a354ec96894920c52104512b72c","tid":493550,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"地球只是一個實驗場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4915830aa6870c7c61a054407a84c92ffef75956","tid":493550,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"智者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}